<li id="cite_note-92"><b><a href="#cite_ref-92" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFBray.5B.5BHans_von_Storch.5D.5D1999">Bray, Dennis; <a href="/wiki/Hans_von_Storch" title="Hans von Storch">Hans von Storch</a> (1999). "<a href="http://coast.gkss.de/staff/storch/pdf/bray_storch_1999.pdf" class="external text" title="http://coast.gkss.de/staff/storch/pdf/bray_storch_1999.pdf" rel="nofollow">Climate Science: An Empirical Example of Postnormal Science</a>" (PDF). <i>Bulletin of the American Meteorological Society</i> <b>80</b>: 439. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1175%2F1520-0477%281999%29080%3C0439%3ACSAEEO%3E2.0.CO%3B2" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1175%2F1520-0477%281999%29080%3C0439%3ACSAEEO%3E2.0.CO%3B2" rel="nofollow">10.1175/1520-0477(1999)080&lt;0439:CSAEEO&gt;2.0.CO;2</a></span><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://coast.gkss.de/staff/storch/pdf/bray_storch_1999.pdf" class="external free" title="http://coast.gkss.de/staff/storch/pdf/bray_storch_1999.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://coast.gkss.de/staff/storch/pdf/bray_storch_1999.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-09-04</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Climate+Science%3A+An+Empirical+Example+of+Postnormal+Science&amp;rft.jtitle=Bulletin+of+the+American+Meteorological+Society&amp;rft.aulast=Bray&amp;rft.aufirst=Dennis&amp;rft.au=Bray%2C+Dennis&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BHans+von+Storch%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=1999&amp;rft.volume=80&amp;rft.pages=439&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1175%2F1520-0477%281999%29080%3C0439%3ACSAEEO%3E2.0.CO%3B2&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcoast.gkss.de%2Fstaff%2Fstorch%2Fpdf%2Fbray_storch_1999.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Scientific_opinion_on_climate_change"><span style="display: none;">&