<li id="cite_note-95"><b><a href="#cite_ref-95" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.fair.org/index.php?page=1156" class="external text" title="http://www.fair.org/index.php?page=1156" rel="nofollow">Steve Rendall, "The Hypocrisy of George Will"</a>, FAIR report, citing the <i><a href="/wiki/San_Francisco_Chronicle" title="San Francisco Chronicle">San Francisco Chronicle</a></i>, 9/27/92.</li>
